profile: Lloyd Empires is an Ottawa proud, locally owned moving and delivery company which provides professional moving and packing services. Local and long distance moving services would be our specialty, while we also thrive in providing reliable commercial and office movers within Ottawa and a large surrounding area. Lloyd Empires long distance movers provide moving services from coast to coast, within Canada. All of our movers and moving services from the local Ottawa area to long distance are professional and hold customers in the highest regard, while still managing to provide some of the most competitive rates among Ottawa movers.
